subject: Dear Sir,
body:
Dear Sir,
I honestly believe that you must have received your full payment from Mr. Daniel S. Raj hence you stopped communicating with me. However, just be honest and tell me if you have received your payment in your bank account or not. This is for our record purposes to conclude your compensation payment fund transaction with the United States government.
Yours Sincerely,
Mrs. Julia William 
Treasuryâ€™s Department.

subject: Re:   Dear Sir,
body:
Hello Mrs. Julia William,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I appreciate your concern about the payment situation with Mr. Daniel S. Raj. However, I'm not quite sure what you're referring to. Could you please provide more details about this? 

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Eileen
